            "answer_text": "Simple compact relation : A + B + AB/100 Since these are discounts, both Ac& B are negative. -10 + (-15) + (-10 x -15)/100 = -25 + 1.50 = -23.50% Negative means net discount. For more on this relation, refer to this post : K S Narayanan's post in Mathematics Unraveled :-) ",
